OL,5, A Nigerian university student arrested 
OL,6, and detained for more than two weeks   
OL,7, after he allegedly defamed President   
OL,8, Muhammadu Buhari's wife on Twitter has 
OL,9, apologised to the first lady.          
OL,11,FAminu Adamu Mohammed was released on   
OL,12,FFriday after authorities dropped the   
OL,13,Fcharges on ''compassionate grounds.".  
OL,15,FMr Mohammed denied spreading ''false'' 
OL,16,Finformation during a court appearance. 
OL,18,FHe denied defaming Aisha Buhari in a   
OL,19,Ftweet suggesting she had misused public
OL,20,Fmoney to her satisfaction.             
